headline: Is There Still Room for Axon’s Stock to Grow After 62% Rally and AI Expansion?
summary: If you’re staring at Axon Enterprise’s stock chart, you might be asking yourself if all the gains are already in the rearview mirror or if there’s plenty of road left ahead. Over the past three years, the stock is up a remarkable 449.8%, and a whopping 564.3% over five years. Even with a 6.8% dip in the last month and a modest 1.4% slip this week, the buzz around Axon hasn’t faded. Year to date, shares are still up 18.1%, and the one-year return is an eye-catching 62.3%.
